MCQs

Q1. Binary Tree Node

A node in Binary trees can have how many children ?

Options
This problem has only one correct answer
(a) 2
(b) any number of children
(c) 0 or 1 or 2
(c) 0 or 1

Ans. (c) 0 or 1 or 2

************************************************************************

Q2. Input Binary Tree
Send Feedback
Consider the below code
takeInput()
    print("Enter root data")
    rootData = int(input())
    if (rootData == -1)
        return None
    root = BinaryTreeNode(rootData)
    root.left = takeInput()
    root.right = takeInput()
    return root
Alt text

What will be the input(excluding -1) to above code to construct this tree ?
 1)  2 7 2 6 5 11 5 9 4 
 2)  2 7 5 6 11 2 5 4 9 
 3)  2 7 5 2 6 9 5 11 4
 
 Options
This problem has only one correct answer
(a) 1
(b) 2
(c) 3

Ans. (a) 1

************************************************************************

Q3. Binary Tree Levelwise

